cs.DB, cs.AI, cs.IR, cs.SE, cs.HC. 

This paper is about a tool that helps users write SPARQL queries on RDF datasets in the LOD cloud. The tool uses auto-complete suggestions based on the queried data and provides suggestions on ways to change the query to better match the needs of the user. This work involves aspects of database systems (cs.DB), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information retrieval (cs.IR), software engineering (cs.SE), and human-computer interaction (cs.HC).
